title: SAM Kameralny Kompleks Gastronomiczny
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European, Polish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Laid-back bakery cafe offering fresh baked bread plus salads, sandwiches, breakfast, fruit and vegetable juices. Also sells some organic products. Always has vegetarian and vegan dishes daily and occasionally vegan dessert, marked. Free Wi-Fi, has English menu.
